events.name: 移動（ラストダンジョン外観）

parameters: Kyle: Lady Lucia, Lady Sylvia...

Kyle: As you wished, we lured Luna here. And then you... you gave her death.
Impressive indeed.

Sylvia: Hehe... Luna's power was unexpected, but she couldn't beat Lord Zena's
immortal body.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe...
Sylvia: Lucia, what will you do with Luna's corpse?
Class10-0a
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] We'll use it as a sacrifice.
Sylvia: A sacrifice? I see, feed it to Hilda?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Feed it to Hilda? Don't be ridiculous. Her flesh is a delicacy.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] The flesh of a sorceress so skilled in magic is special.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] With her flesh, we can create a wonderful new spell. Hehehe...

Sylvia: I see. Use it as meat for the sacrifice. It's perfect for Luna. Now I
understand why you've been keeping it so carefully. Heheheh
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehehe... Ahahahahaha!
Sylvia: Ahahahahaha!
Kyle: ...
Sylvia: Kyle, you've done a good job this time too.
Kyle: Yes. Lady Lucia... Lady Sylvia... Everything is as you wish...
Kyle: With this, we are also safe.

Kyle: Lady Lucia, Lady Sylvia... We, the resistance of Norvanna, will only
pretend to oppose you.
Kyle: We will cooperate where we can... that's the deal.
Sylvia: What a good boy.
Kyle: Lady Sylvia, as usual, may I have a kiss on the forehead...
Sylvia: Hehe... Today, I'll give you one on the lips, specially.
Sylvia: Mmm... Mmmm... Puhah
Kyle: Mmm... Ah... Thank you very much.
Sylvia: Hehehe...
